# thoth_policy_sync

Triggers `POST /:tenant-id/thoth/policies/sync` and tracks sync status from
`GET /:tenant-id/thoth/policies/sync/status`.

## Example Usage

```terraform
resource "thoth_policy_sync" "default" {
  trigger             = "post-policy-update"
  wait_for_completion = true
  poll_interval_seconds = 5
  timeout_seconds       = 180
}
```
